### create chat
@token = {{signin.response.body.token}}
POST http://localhost:6688/api/chats
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "name": "acme",
    "members": [1, 2],
    "public": false
}

### get chat list

GET http://localhost:6688/api/chats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### get user list

GET http://localhost:6688/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
